    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Mr. Nease",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Mr. J. Edgar Hoover,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Washington, D.C.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "Dear Mr. Hoover:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "The enclosed came to my husband yesterday.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "After reading it aloud to the family, as a good example",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "of crack-pot-ism, advertising or what have you, he threw",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "it into the wastebasket. I retrieved it, thinking it might",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "better go into your wastebasket than ours, examined by",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "your department en route thither, as of possible value.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "I presume several thousand have been mailed, and you may",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "receive numberless duplicates. I will risk that.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "as an economist at Columbia University receives many strange",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "missives. This is as strange a one as has come for some",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "time, and very appropriate to the present moment.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "Sincerely yours,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
